  "body": "<div id=\"post-view110128796059\" class=\"post-view pcol2 _param(1) _postViewArea110128796059\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t \r\n<p>간단한 성형수술을 할 때,</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>내시경 검사시 수면내시경을 하게 될 때,</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>받게 되는 수면마취가 있습니다. </p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>간단하고 큰 부작용이 없다고 알려져 있죠. </p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>이번에 대한의사협회에서 2008년말부터 2011년까지 </p>\r\n<p>수면마취 사고 건수가 모두 23건이었다고 발표했습니다. </p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>그 중 18명은 숨졌고, 5명은 뇌손상과 전신마비를 비롯한 심각한 장애를 입었다고 밝혔다. </p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/e72d416a4e688099.jpg\" width=\"230\" height=\"219\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rwidth: 230px; rheight: 219px\" id=\"20120112_278/isuhani_13263506663949bYzt_JPEG/imagesCA8N1IX4.jpg\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A430119B')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/e72d416a4e688099.jpg\"><br style=\"CLEAR: both\" /><br style=\"CLEAR: both\" /></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>관련기사. </p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><a class=\"con_link\" href=\"http://www.ytn.co.kr/_ln/0103_201201120640205728\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.ytn.co.kr/_ln/0103_201201120640205728</a></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/ac224b1708382ef5.jpg\" width=\"190\" height=\"266\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rwidth: 190px; rheight: 266px\" id=\"20120112_147/isuhani_1326350666911vWxwH_JPEG/imagesCA1X5PMI.jpg\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A430119B')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/ac224b1708382ef5.jpg\"></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>",
